{"tid":404231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【澳門立選】澳網媒指有人票站外派錢　廉署證接投訴：未必構成賄選","createTime":"2017-09-18T02:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T03:33:26.000Z","uid":53379,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46c2a730ec6832fd6fb436ebdf2754295d7a9e27","tid":404231,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【澳門立選】澳網媒指有人票站外派錢　廉署證接投訴：未必構成賄選</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170917/s00001/9fb2aff8e2e1e6a5ea12b697c3f3e081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F9fb2aff8e2e1e6a5ea12b697c3f3e081.jpg&h=9769316e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳門立法會選舉投票日已於晚上9時結束，今屆投票人數踴躍，至晚上8時已有168,073人投票，投票率為55%，幾乎已追平去屆總投票率55.02%。澳門網媒「愛瞞日報」指，發現在北區鏡平中學票站外，有人疑似在選民投票後即場派錢。<br />\n<br />\n澳門廉署至今日下午3時接到18宗有關選舉的投訴，其中一宗屬疑似賄選。廉政專員張永春表示有關個案在網上流傳，個案經評估未必構成以金錢交換選票的賄選，將進一步蒐集資料調查。<br />\n<br />\n張永春指出，這宗個案是由候選組別駐票站人員投訴，事發於上午10時，廉署12時許收到投訴。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有團體被指早上為投票後的長者提供早餐，包括飲品及麵包，張永春認為不足以構成打動選民的利益，廉署不視為賄選情況。<br />\n<br />\n澳門選管會主席唐曉峰下午會見傳媒時亦被問到涉嫌派錢情況，他回應稱與廉署密切接觸，「畀錢方面，廉署話搵唔到咁嘅情況」，至於有指有人向選民提供水或飲品，他則稱對於這些物品能否賄賂選民意向，「似乎有啲疑問」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170917/s00001/1505654094495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F1505654094495&d=Mcz9M%2FyZoDcXS3Cg2jQswS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1f3d59cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F1505654094495&h=f4d37f94\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170917/s00001/1505654094495</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4491eb1028f282f36a81b38358b2a6d4d15a223f","tid":404231,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af48ccba131aabc895e0dadf1d75eb3a3a384584","tid":404231,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"明目張膽到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cc2f31d5b7be312950a3323e9445a11de89e96","tid":404231,"uid":23764,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:54:24.000Z","msg":"這就是澳門市"},{"pid":"95774c5e7dac1f3b37e4f69f1c8ac84a71b54c78","tid":404231,"uid":38194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"澳門狗就係咁，咪理鳩佢地啦"},{"pid":"ce817d8883c86d9b95211274113b89b857ea495c","tid":404231,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"咁都唔算, 點先算, 要佢地派錢果緊大大聲講自己賄選緊??"},{"pid":"81a616e9cd0c31dcd35e5c42975233006db71227","tid":404231,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"澳門係咪強姦只要體外射精都告唔入??"},{"pid":"0fb8610e4d19290f4c4d6d5964f291073334ce2f","tid":404231,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:05:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86e3459e1b1c16cb767f7206c0a33a0561587368","tid":404231,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"支那人做廉政專員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b241d0d3261099d1c44c34b3a8fdb2cabd89f40d","tid":404231,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"3a449f6f85838f6a341b8ebfe290b4a9c54880d5","tid":404231,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"浸撚死哂佢地就啱"},{"pid":"fb83cad381fd126334fb994312c117c5855cf950","tid":404231,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"有得你叫CCAC<br />\nCan't Catch Any